{"tid":2156588,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港窮人地獄，係因為政府取消咗遺產稅！","createTime":"2020-08-14T14:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T14:57:40.000Z","uid":72795,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"84936a9187477ee2e8f7acdddd63bbb01bed2a89","tid":2156588,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「<strong><span class=\"red\">香港於二零零五年取消了遺產稅，香港從此再無真正意義的直接稅，香港的稅政制度邪惡而荒謬，成為全世界富豪的天堂，成為中國土豪的洗腳盆，香港居民為此付出了慘重的代價。</span></strong>這一切，必須結束了。香港必須建立以遺產稅、贈予稅、離境稅、房產稅等直接稅為主體的新型稅政結構。讓食利者感到羞恥，讓勞動者感到光榮。我們必須讓香港重新成為創業者和創造價值者的天堂。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-08/19/36007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-08%2F19%2F36007.html&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcRY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=65b6b540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-08/19/36007.html</a>"},{"pid":"2f9a08915efc4a9d3bed064cdff620a30faa9d10","tid":2156588,"uid":41368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"交埋交埋俾黑驚買冰定填海整高鐵"},{"pid":"83ac73fba4a46d9a84176547bc108ac400ea453d","tid":2156588,"uid":259901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"加稅=交錢比正苦<br />\n傻的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb17294add75f402facbc8abe52e8795f5b32f4d","tid":2156588,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cc5abe840b4525b8b8d9a8e940135784447c44","tid":2156588,"uid":4503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"簡單d 800 萬以下 遺產唔使交<br />\n<br />\n死前7年內